title: #92Noon! VikesXmas/Talkers/ZimZoom/Bishop/Glee
description: Another edition of "12 Days of Vikings Christmas" in the first hour, Mike Zimmer's presser, Charch & SI's Greg Bishop get us to the final when Aaron Gleeman joins to chat about the NBA/Wolves as their season gets started this week!
